but I hope this video helped answer some
your questions on how you might fill

00:07:15.989 --> 00:07:19.399
something like a button that doesn't
have a flat back or something that

00:07:19.399 --> 00:07:21.830
doesn't actually have a bezel edge that's
just

00:07:21.830 --> 00:07:23.519
a flat straight drop edge

